text: Yahya Abdul-Mateen II (born 1986) is an American actor. He is best known for his role Cadillac in the television series The Get Down. He also starred in Baywatch (2017). He also appeared in The Greatest Showman and DC's Aquaman as Black Manta. Abdul-Mateen was born in New Orleans, Louisiana. Before acting, Abdul-Mateen was an architect. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Living people Category:1986 births Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:American architects Category:Actors from New Orleans
